    <h1 class="mt-10 font-bold text-2xl">Hi.</h1>
    <p>I'm Jeremy.</p>
    <p>I like to make things.</p>
    <p>Sometimes I even finish them.</p>

    <h1 class="mt-10 font-bold text-2xl">Featured Project</h1>
    <InReview client:load />

